data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of tranquility! This captivating two-story residence, located at the end of a charming cul-de-sac, invites you to experience the epitome of comfort and style.  Step inside and be greeted by the stairway to your humble abode or to your living room and dining room that effortlessly creates an inviting atmosphere for both formality and entertaining.         Or proceed with excitement to your family room that sits right off the kitchen and allows you to engage with your guests or family as you e are preparing your favorite meal. The abundant natural light enhances the warm and welcoming ambiance throughout.  Your culinary aspirations will come to life in the well-appointed kitchen with ample counter space. The convenience of a half bathroom downstairs adds a touch of practicality to the layout.          As you venture upstairs to discover four generously sized bedrooms, offering the perfect retreat for rest and rejuvenation. The master suite boasts a luxurious feel, complete with an ensuite bathroom for added privacy and a separate sitting area for your leisure.  But the allure doesn't end indoors; step outside to your backyard looking at the pristine greenery of the adjacent golf course. The perfect backdrop for serene evenings and vibrant gatherings with family and friends.          One of the many highlights of this residence is its location in a quiet community without the constraints of an HOA. Enjoy the freedom to personalize and enhance your living space without the typical restrictions.      Seize the opportunity to make this house your home where modern comfort meets serene surroundings.     This is a STEAL OF A DEAL.........Schedule a viewing today and discover the lifestyle that awaits you in this idyllic haven!
